# Guidelines for new screens
- Use Expo-specific features if necessary
- Use arrow function for components
- Use Typescript interfaces to define props
- Use Tailwind styling for TWRNC and Tailwind colors
- You can use any iOS-specific design feature (this app is iOS only)
- Use pre-existing components if necessary
- Use Expo vector icons for icons